OL,3,C'Explosions were going off' - Battery
OL,4,Cwarning after bin lorry fires
OL,6,FJulia Barthram went to find out more
OL,7,Fabout the dangers posed by not
OL,8,Fdisposing of lithium batteries
OL,9,Fcorrectly.
OL,11,FPeople are being warned about the
OL,12,Fdangers of throwing lithium batteries
OL,13,Fin the bin following a series of lorry
OL,14,Ffires.
OL,16,FTwo bin wagons in County Durham have
OL,17,Fgone on fire in the last month - in
OL,18,FSedgefield and Wolsingham - due to
OL,19,Fvapes and batteries which have been
OL,20,Fdisposed of incorrectly.
