OL,3,C'Explosions were going off' - Battery
OL,4,Cwarning after bin lorry fires
OL,6,FIt brings the total to four this year
OL,7,Fand 12 since 2019-2020.
OL,9,FThe lorries had to carry out an
OL,10,Femergency tip of their load after the
OL,11,Ffires broke out inside the wagons.
OL,13,FDurham County Council said the issue
OL,14,Fis putting its bin crews at risk.
