OL,6,FCraig Wilson, who was driving a lorry
OL,7,Fwhen it went on fire in Weardale
OL,8,Fearlier this month, said: "I first
OL,9,Fnoticed the smoke when we were in
OL,10,FWolsingham, just down from the school.
OL,11,FWe thought best get it out the way,
OL,12,Fout of the town centre and away from
OL,13,Fthe school.
