OL,3,C'Explosions were going off' - Battery
OL,4,Cwarning after bin lorry fires
OL,6,F"Within 30 seconds to a minute it just
OL,7,Ftook off and it was away then.
OL,8,FObviously the fire brigade was called.
OL,9,FWhile we were waiting for them there
OL,10,Fwere a lot of explosions going off at
OL,11,Fthe time - whatever was in the load
OL,12,Fwas going off. It was quite loud and
OL,13,Fquite scary really."
OL,15,FCouncillor Mark Wilkes, from Durham
OL,16,FCounty Council, said: "It really has
OL,17,Fbecome quite a serious issue now and
OL,18,Fwe really need people to listen to how
OL,19,Fthey're supposed to recycle properly."
