OL,6,F"You get blow torch like flames, so a
OL,7,Fsmall fire rapidly can become a very
OL,8,Flarge fire and in a bin lorry such as
OL,9,Fthe one behind us, it can take out the
OL,10,Fbin lorry.
OL,12,FHow should vapes and batteries be
OL,13,Fdisposed of?
OL,15,FDurham County Council runs a small
OL,16,Felectrical recycling scheme. People
OL,17,Fcan leave batteries and vapes at
OL,18,Fcollection points at 161 collection
OL,19,Fpoints around the county.
