OL,6,FThe small Waste Electrical and
OL,7,FElectronic Equipment (WEEE) recycling
OL,8,Fpoints are at community venues and
OL,9,Fprimary schools.
OL,11,FThere are also 75 vape recycling
OL,12,Fpoints in community venues.
OL,14,FSome supermarkets also offer a service
OL,15,Fto help people dispose of batteries
OL,16,Fsafely.
OL,18,FThey can also be taken to household
OL,19,Fwaste recycling centres.
